Available Tools: create_deal | update_deal_stage | get_deal | list_deals_by_stage | close_deal
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "deal_id": "string", "contact_id": "string", "stage": "string", "value": number }
Response Schema: { "deal_id": "string", "name": "string", "stage": "string", "value": number, "probability": number }
---
Question: Establish a new prospect deal D-3001 for contact C-5001 valued at 25000.
Call: { "func_call": "create_deal", "deal_id": "D-3001", "contact_id": "C-5001", "stage": "prospect", "value": 25000 }
Response: { "deal_id": "D-3001", "name": "Globex Expansion Plan", "stage": "prospect", "value": 25000, "probability": 10 }

Question: Shift deal D-3002 to the qualified stage for contact C-5002 with an updated value of 55000.
Call: { "func_call": "update_deal_stage", "deal_id": "D-3002", "contact_id": "C-5002", "stage": "qualified", "value": 55000 }
Response: { "deal_id": "D-3002", "name": "Stark Robotics Contract", "stage": "qualified", "value": 55000, "probability": 40 }

Question: Promote deal D-3003 to proposal for contact C-5003, maintaining the value at 135000.
Call: { "func_call": "update_deal_stage", "deal_id": "D-3003", "contact_id": "C-5003", "stage": "proposal", "value": 135000 }
Response: { "deal_id": "D-3003", "name": "Wayne Tower Renovation", "stage": "proposal", "value": 135000, "probability": 60 }

